    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p><monospace>KerrBam</monospace>
      (<xref alt="Palumbo et al., 2022" rid="ref-Palumbo_2022" ref-type="bibr">Palumbo
      et al., 2022</xref>): An analytical raytracing code for equatorial
